                    <h3>Classic Copper Kettle</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/copper-kettle.webp" alt="Copper kettle">
                    <p>A tried and tested copper kettle with a classic rustic aesthetic.</p>
                    <p>Price: R450.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Ceramic Mug</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/ceramic-mug.webp" alt="Ceramic mug">
                    <p>Hot chocolate will taste great in this.</p>
                    <p>Price: R180.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Basket</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/basket.webp" alt="Basket">
                    <p>Perfect for putting stuff in.</p>
                    <p>Price: R80.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Clay Flowerpot</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/clay-flowerpot.webp" alt="Clay flowerpot">
                    <p>This pot is perfect for flowers or even small trees.</p>
                    <p>Price: R888.00</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Leather Journal</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/leather-journal.webp" alt="Leather journal">
                    <p>
                        This can be used to write things down.
                        Handcrafted with premium homemade leather
                        (ethically sourced from animals with their written consent).
                    </p>
                    <p>Price: R175.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Leather Wallet</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/leather-wallet.webp" alt="Leather wallet">
                    <p>
                        Do you suffer from too much pocket space? Try putting your money in this!
                    </p>
                    <p>Price: R150.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Metal Windchime</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/metal-windchime.webp" alt="Metal windchime">
                    <p>It makes a jingling sound when the wind blows, your neighbours will love it.</p>
                    <p>Price: R420.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Wood Bowl</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/wood-bowl.webp" alt="Wood bowl">
                    <p>Perfect for putting stuff inside of.</p>
                    <p>Price: R350.00</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Wood Chopping Board</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/wood-chopping-board.webp" alt="Wood chopping board">
                    <p>This is sort of like a helmet, but it's for your kitchen counter.</p>
                    <p>Price: R550.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Paper Lantern</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/paper-lantern.webp" alt="Paper lantern">
                    <p>It's light because it's made of paper, helps to see when it's dark.</p>
                    <p>Price: R770.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Glass Vase</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/glass-vase.webp" alt="Glass vase">
                    <p>This is where the flowers go when you want them inside the house.</p>
                    <p>Price: R1337.00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Woolie Blanket</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/woolie-blanket.webp" alt="Woolie blanket">
                    <p>A warm and cozy blanket made from 100% real wool sourced 100% from real handcrafted jerseys.</p>
                    <p>Price: R2500.00</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="craftwork-item">
                    <h3>Wooden Birdhouse</h3>
                    <img src="~/images/MyCrafts/wood-birdhouse.webp" alt="Wood birdhouse">
